data.description: Immaculate 2 bedroom plus den and loft 2.5 bath 1 car garage lakefront townhome in Coral Lakes.  This southern exposure property built in 2007 boasts tons of upgrades and almost 1400sf of living area, updated kitchen with solid surface countertops and upgraded cabinets, tile flooring in the large living areas, high ceilings, spacious bedrooms, new AC with 12 year transferable warranty, tile roof, and lush landscaping.  New Hurricaine impact rated windows and sliders throuout installed in 2023 with transferrable warranty.  The community is well established with guard gate, pool areas, clubhouse fitness center and more.  Great location close to restaurants, shopping and schools!!
